@startuml
title Graduate Query Sequence
participant ChatApplicationService
participant GraduateRoutePlannerPort
participant route-aware conversation context
participant "Retrieval Port" as retrieval
database PostgreSQL
ChatApplicationService -> GraduateRoutePlannerPort : interpret
GraduateRoutePlannerPort --> ChatApplicationService : typed result/fallback
ChatApplicationService -> route-aware conversation context : resolve
ChatApplicationService -> retrieval : retrieveContext(query)
retrieval -> PostgreSQL : parameterized SQL
PostgreSQL --> retrieval : rows
retrieval --> ChatApplicationService : context + citations
@enduml
